release_note: The problem of the login screen being displayed at startup has been resolved. The method of selecting the type of feelyou has been changed to a tap method: press and hold the feelyou button and then tap to select.
Fixed a minor bug. Improved performance.
The DM function has been discontinued.
Temporary release of Premium Plan features.
In this update we have fixed the following issues: Unable to send DM stickers Unable to reply on specific device models
Minor updates fixes
Fixed problems with new registration and login.
In the Japanese version of the application some links on the settings page have been updated.
The screen will now automatically refresh when blocking a user.

You can now check the graphs by watching ads. The translation button is now displayed on all posts. Added boosting feature. When you boost after posting your post will appear at the top in the Boost timeline. This is for when you have happy news or something you want everyone to listen. You can use this with Premium membership or by watching ads.
Added a language filter to the timeline. Added a guide to show that you can translate by tapping the translation icon when you first start the application.

New The Planet is back with a little new look. The criteria for getting trees has been simplified. You can see it from the tree icon on My Page. We ve introduced a filter on the notification page. You can now filter the notifications you want to see. Improvements Fixed a bug that prevented the language filter from being kept.
DM is back!
You can now follow hashtags. You can now receive notifications when a post is made using a hashtag you have followed.

With this update we improved the following: Added usage history to the hashtag input screen. The community has been replaced by hashtags so we hope you ll continue to use them! You can now post from the hashtag timeline. Fixed a bug in the display of the private post icon.

Feelyou App Ver.3 is here! Implemented Hashtag instead of Community to make it easier to find common topics. Improved Mood labels . It s now easier to express your current mood than before. Added a new concept Act of Kindness . We plan to visualize the accumulation of your kind actions in the app and plant trees according to this number. We look forward to your feedback! hello feelyou.app
Fixed the tap area of the three dot menu in the mood post. Improved detection of false positives when Feelyou tap.

Added the Hot tab In this tab the posts are listed in the order of the most recent comments. Visit this tab when you want to join in a friendly conversation with others or when you want to see what other users are talking about. We are working on an update to make the app more helpful for everyone. Hope you feel free to give us feedback Added a checkmark for your language only Now you can filter by language settings on your phone!

Improved the order of tabs in the timeline! After many requests we set Everyone to the main page. Improved the name from Feelyoumore to Follow! Changed the name to be shorter and easier to understand. Other minor bug fixes

Switchable the publish destination everyone private for anonymous posts after posting. Notified when there is a new comment on a post you have feelyou commented on. If annoyed switchable to push notifications in the settings screen.
Fix a bug when changing email. Hide the in app notification when a tree is acquired.
Fix minor bug
Fix minor bugs.
Improved the behavior when updating your profile. Fixed the passcode setting could not be turned off.
Russian in the body of the post is now displayed naturally. Russian language in the body of the message is now displayed naturally. Fixed minor bugs.
Fixed a bug in the CommunityPage.
Fixed a bug in the Mypage.

Improvements You can now filter language and moods in the FeelyouMore and community timeline! You can now select the community on the posting page. So many Feelyousers have requested this and we hope you use it!
Fixed the following bugs: Fixed a bug that caused the app to crash when tapping a community tag. Fixed a bug in the reply time display.
Improvement Filters are now available on the community page. Speed up! Community FeelyouMore

NEW Drafts of posts are now automatically saved! Improvement Speed up! Timeline MyPage Modal popup Corrected the item names on the community page. Display the latest post date and time in the community list. Notification of the new community is now shown in the announcement. Fixed a bug where the display would not refresh after blocking or reporting.
Improvements Added language filter to tag filter and community filter timeline. Fixed a bug in the mood filter. Improved the speed of MyDiary display after launching the app.

NEW We ve added a mood filter! Previously you could only select one emotion but now you can select multiple emotions simultaneously! Bug fix Improvements We re working on speed improvements now! Let us know how it goes. Overall speed improvement iOS Faster speed when transitioning to the post details screen UX improvement by introducing skeleton loading
NEW You can now filter by tags Mood history is added to MyDiary Bug fix Improvements Fixed bugs in DM keyboard display and picture sending. Improved the speed of the first registration.
NEW You can now post Music Link! Bug Fixes and Improvements Mainly for newly registered users! Added description to the posting option. Added labels at the bottom menu. Fixed other minor bugs.
The following bugs have been fixed! Bug in which past data cannot be acquired in MyPage TimeLine. The background color of the notification list and announcement list is white in dark mode.

NEW You can now filter the timeline by your language. Improvements Fixed a bug that caused the freezing of the app when you got a tree . Happy mood tracking in the new version! Share your ideas in the comments and rate Feelyou!

Bug fix Improvements Fixed a bug that images could not be expanded in DM Fixed a bug that prevented opening the app from push notifications. Added a space above the Feelyou button Changed the tag icon Added tags in the user post list Fixed other minor bugs

Hey there. With this update we have renewed the design to pursue our goal that the app aims for. Our goal is to make mental care easy and fun for everyone. We ll be working on it step by step so please look forward to our next update! We re looking forward to your feedback!

How s everyone doing In this update we ve improved the following! Improved app s running tab switching MyPage settings page Planet page etc. . Please let me know how it goes! MyDiary posts are now grouped by date.
Thanks for using Feelyou! This update contains some bug fixes and performance improvements. Feelyou helps you to record your precious moments and connect with others who have been there.
Bug fix Improvements The translation button is not displayed for posts in your own language. Fixed a bug related to the display of notifications.

NEW Now you can express your empathy more freely! Press and hold the Feelyou icon to select each one. Feelyou Hug GoodLuck Wow Happy THX Bug fix Improvements Adjusted the height of the comment form You can now receive a push notification when a new group is created. Fixed minor bugs
Hey folks! With this update we ve fixed some bugs improved the stability of the app.

NEW Added a weekly bar chart to the monthly report There s three iPhone widgets to choose from: Add your mood by simply tapping the mood icon See your recent mood entries right on your home screen See your posted days to keep posting and get to know the real you Bug fix Improvements After posting on the same day the posting button at the top of the main screen will be hidden. Fixed minor bugs
Fixed a bug that prevented scrolling in the emotion filter timeline.

NEW Whole UI UX of the timeline on the main page has been changed. You can now switch between private and public after mood posting. Bug fix Improvements Improvements of the performance of My page. The app will now automatically reconnect when a network error occurs. You can now check the monthly report for the last month or more.

We re always working on making the app better for Feelyousers!! This update includes: You can now choose whether or not to accept comments from other users. You can now translate each post on a timeline. You can now block users from anonymous posts.

We re always working on making the app better for Feelyousers. This update includes: UI improvements of each community page Fix the problems about the number of post on My Page Feelyou reaction is now richer Try to tap!
Happy New Year! We hope you re loving Feelyou. This update includes: App performance improvements Free users also can now check the mood history graph
Improvements of speed to display the community screen
App icon has been changed winter version. Fixed the bug that a red mark under user icon is at wrong position.
NEW You can now check helpful self care quotes in the Monthly Report! Hooray! Renewal the subscription page. Check it out!

New Features You can check the mood ratio of the joining community. Notify you when your friend starts to use Feelyou by your invitation. New Have you followed Feelyou s Twitter Instagram and Facebook Added those accounts link in My Page Settings. Please follow comment! Bug fix Fixed an issue that some users can t receive push notifications. Please restart the app after updating to 1.10.1 to apply this fix.

New features Better community page You can now see a list of your joined communities. You can now filter by category and language. New communities are now picked up. Bug fixes and improvements Improvements of the mood post page. Fixed the problem that auto scroll does not work well when tapping the Home icon at the bottom.

New features You can now lock the app with PIN code! Set on Setting page Privacy. You can now delete replies of your posts. You can now search a community by its name. Fixed the bug that screen is refreshed while you scroll community posts list down.
Bug fixes and improvements Fix the issue that user can t sign in by google social login.

New features Monthly summary is available! Reflect on your mood history for the last month. For premium You can now turn on off the dark mode on the app s settings page. Bug fixes and improvements Fixed the bug that you couldn t Feelyou on a post displayed by tapping on a notification. In the Communities tab you can now see the posts of the communities you have joined. You can now see the Community List page in the bottom menu. The Planet page has been moved to the settings page.

New features Private post function is released as a free feature. Other users can not see them. Japanese users can filter posts by languages. The guide tour is added for people starting to use feelyou at the first time. Bug fixes improvements Fixed WeeklyMood display bugs Fixed DM stamp keyboard display bugs

New features You can search for friends from the settings page You can switch notifications on off for each community. The number of posts per month is shown in the calendar. Improvement of the notifications list UI. Bug fixes improvements Community pages now load faster. Fixed a bug where mood patterns were not displayed in some cases. Other minor problems fixed
Dark Mode is available now!! Requires iOS 13.0 or later and don t forget to activate dark mode in device settings.

New features For Premium Create your community! Share your feelings about the topics you are interested in. You can now share your mood graphs with friends! You can now turn on off push notifications in detail from the My Page Settings page. Bug fixes improvements You can now translate replies!! Five randomly picked posts are inserted into the ALL timeline! You won t miss a post that is related to you. We show you the modal window to ask for reviews and feedback. Add a special icon to our official accounts Feelyou Support UX improvements WeeklyMood and LineChart For users registered by August 31 You can check whether the current premium feature was given away by us as a promotional campaign.

Hi there how are you feeling We re sure you ll choose Amazing because we ve added a lot of new features!!
